010/extras/66c657e0e1934683355465f422371743.mp4?t=1745838151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Navigate through a massive underwater base, complete intricate puzzles, and solve an ancient secret concealed at the bottom of the ocean. BONE TOTEM features the same isometric, point-and-click gameplay that made STASIS a classic fan favorite, but with a new cast and a unique setting that will leave you gasping for breath.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426010/extras/00cbe0ba75892b598ebc435ad45a3353.poster.avif?t=1745838151\" width=628 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426010/extras/00cbe0ba75892b598ebc435ad45a3353.webm?t=1745838151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426010/extras/00cbe0ba75892b598ebc435ad45a3353.mp4?t=1745838151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With stunning visuals, a music score by Mark Morgan, a screenplay written by a Hollywood ace, voice acting by veteran actors, and a gripping storyline that will keep you on the edge of your seat - STASIS: BONE TOTEM is a must-play game for horror and sci-fi adventure fans.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426010/extras/b7bd9573b5f6c959a55262090dc287dc.poster.avif?t=1745838151\" width=628 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426010/extras/b7bd9573b5f6c959a55262090dc287dc.webm?t=1745838151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426010/extras/b7bd9573b5f6c959a55262090dc287dc.mp4?t=1745838151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>So what are you waiting for? Dive into the unknown and uncover the BONE TOTEM beneath the waves.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426010/extras/d6de265c34c0966af0cb33255b461f2e.poster.avif?t=1745838151\" width=628 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426010/extras/d6de265c34c0966af0cb33255b461f2e.webm?t=1745838151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426010/extras/d6de265c34c0966af0cb33255b461f2e.mp4?t=1745838151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
